---
import CaseStudyLayout from "../layouts/CaseStudyLayout.astro";
---

<CaseStudyLayout
  title="Upwave — Health & Wellness Platform"
  description="How I led product and design for Upwave — Turner's health and wellness venture — from concept to 1 million users in 8 months."
  ogImage="/images/upwave/turner-upwave-site.png"
>
  <style>
    :root {
      --upwave-orange: #f26522;
      --upwave-red: #c83c2c;
      --upwave-gold: #f5a623;
      --upwave-dark: #1e1e1e;
      --warm-white: #f7f5f2;
      --soft-cream: #fff8f4;
      --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
      --text-secondary: #5a5a5a;
      --text-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      --accent: #f26522;
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 90vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      background: linear-gradient(
        160deg,
        #1a1a1a 0%,
        #202020 40%,
        #151515 100%
      );
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: -10%;
      left: -10%;
      width: 800px;
      height: 800px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(
        circle,
        rgba(242, 101, 34, 0.12) 0%,
        transparent 70%
      );
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .hero-left {
      max-width: 800px;
      z-index: 1;
      margin-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .hero-right {
      z-index: 1;
      width: 100%;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero-right img {
      max-width: 900px;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 64px 128px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .hero-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--upwave-orange);
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 84px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-light);
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ── Platform Showcase (warm bg) ── */
    .platform {
      background: var(--soft-cream);
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .platform-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 80px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .platform-card {
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(242, 101, 34, 0.06);
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.8, 0.2, 1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
    }

    .platform-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: 0 32px 64px rgba(242, 101, 34, 0.1);
    }

    .platform-card img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .platform-card-text {
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .platform-card-text h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .platform-card-text p {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Dark section ── */
    .dark-section {
      background: var(--upwave-dark);
      padding: 160px 80px;
    }

    .dark-section .section-label {
      color: var(--upwave-gold);
    }
    .dark-section .section-heading {
      color: #fff;
    }
    .dark-section .section-body {
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    .dark-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
      margin-top: 80px;
      max-width: 1300px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
    }

    .dark-card {
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      transition: all 0.4s ease;
    }

    .dark-card img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .dark-card-text {
      padding: 32px;
    }

    .dark-card-text h3 {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 500;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .dark-card-text p {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 300;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    }

    /* ── Campaign / Brand ── */
    .campaign {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2e1d1a 100%);
      padding: 160px 80px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 100px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .campaign-image {
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 32px 64px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }

    .campaign-image img {
      width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .campaign-text .section-heading {
      color: #fff;
    }
    .campaign-text .section-body {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .hero {
        padding: 120px 32px;
      }
      .hero-left {
        margin-bottom: 48px;
      }
      .platform {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }
      .platform-grid {
        gap: 48px;
      }
      .dark-section {
        padding: 100px 32px;
      }
      .dark-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
      }
      .campaign {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        padding: 100px 32px;
        gap: 64px;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <div class="hero-label">Upwave</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Building a Platform That Makes Wellness Stick</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        I led product and design for Turner's health and wellness venture —
        partnering with IDEO on market validation, then taking it from concept
        to 1M monthly users in eight months.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-right">
      <img
        src="/images/upwave/turner-upwave-site.png"
        alt="Upwave homepage on desktop and mobile"
      />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Context -->
  <section class="context">
    <div class="context-inner">
      <div>
        <div class="section-label">The Challenge</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">
          Pioneering health and wellness in the early IoT era.
        </h2>
        <p class="section-body">
          Upwave was Turner's IoT-driven digital health venture, exploring the
          intersection of quantified-self data and personalized content. As Vice
          President, Product & UX, I led the specialized teams responsible for
          taking the venture from concept to market. Partnering with IDEO for
          initial market validation, I established the product strategy and
          introduced a lean methodology that enabled daily release cycles,
          accelerating growth to 1M monthly unique users in just eight months.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="meta-grid">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>My Role</h4>
            <p>Vice President, Product &amp; UX</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Platform</h4>
            <p>Upwave (Internal Venture)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Scope</h4>
            <p>Product Leadership, Lean Methodology, Team Directorship</p>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <h4>Outcomes</h4>
            <p>0 to 1M Users in 8 mos, Webby Nomination</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Platform Showcase -->
  <div class="platform">
    <div class="section-label">The Platform</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">
      An ecosystem of content, challenges, and analytics.
    </h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      I directed the product roadmap and user experience strategy across the
      entire Upwave ecosystem, guiding teams to ensure a seamless integration
      between media consumption and health tracking behaviors.
    </p>

    <div class="platform-grid">
      <div class="platform-card">
        <img
          src="/images/upwave/8dc0f0d910df1c24b3620919604df9b218d4ad07_190917_110730.png"
          alt="Upwave content platform desktop and mobile"
        />
        <div class="platform-card-text">
          <h3>Content Strategy & Platform</h3>
          <p>
            Directed the UX strategies for a responsive media platform built to
            drive engagement and recirculation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="platform-card">
        <img
          src="/images/upwave/upwave_challenge_screens_desktop_mobile.webp"
          alt="Upwave challenge feature"
        />
        <div class="platform-card-text">
          <h3>Behavioral Challenges</h3>
          <p>
            Oversaw the design framework for multi-day wellness challenges,
            applying behavioral science to daily progress tracking.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="platform-card full-width">
        <img
          src="/images/upwave/turner-upwave-trackit.png"
          alt="Upwave TrackIt analytics dashboard"
        />
        <div class="platform-card-text">
          <h3>TrackIt Analytics</h3>
          <p>
            Guided the strategic integration of emerging wearables and fitness
            trackers with a unified personal health dashboard.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Validation & Process (dark) -->
  <div class="dark-section">
    <div class="section-label">Market Validation & Delivery</div>
    <h2 class="section-heading">From validation to daily releases.</h2>
    <p class="section-body">
      Building a platform at the forefront of quantified-self technology
      (pre-Apple Watch) required rigorous methodology. I initiated a partnership
      with IDEO to secure product-market fit and validate key assumptions before
      large-scale investment. Working cross-functionally, I led the transition
      of the teams to a lean product methodology, establishing a cadence of
      daily release cycles that increased platform recirculation from 5% to 24%.
    </p>

    <div class="dark-grid">
      <div class="dark-card">
        <img
          src="/images/upwave/turner-upwave-ux-01b-1024x587.png"
          alt="Upwave UX wireframes"
        />
        <div class="dark-card-text">
          <h3>Architecture Directorship</h3>
          <p>
            Directed the UX and product teams to establish the foundational
            information architecture and component strategy.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dark-card">
        <img
          src="/images/upwave/turner-upwave-ux-02-1024x768.png"
          alt="Upwave UX design documentation"
        />
        <div class="dark-card-text">
          <h3>Interaction Systems</h3>
          <p>
            Managed multidisciplinary teams ensuring complex health data
            intersections were logically translated into accessible interfaces.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Prior Turner Role / Innovation Leadership -->
  <section
    class="context"
    style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a1a 0%, #2e1d1a 100%);"
  >
    <div class="context-inner" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
      <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <div class="section-label" style="color: var(--upwave-gold);">
          Emerging Technology
        </div>
        <h2 class="section-heading" style="color: #fff;">
          Defining the future of broadcast.
        </h2>
        <p class="section-body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);">
          Prior to leading Upwave, my tenure at Turner included serving as
          Senior Director of Innovation & Emerging Technology spanning CNN,
          Cartoon Network, TBS & TNT. I led multi-disciplinary R&D teams that
          pioneered early mobile augmented reality applications and the
          sync-to-TV technology that ultimately won a Primetime Emmy Award.
          These efforts resulted in two granted U.S. patents for automatic
          content recognition. I also collaborated on the design of the CNN
          "Magic Wall," introducing a massive multi-touch paradigm that
          redefined data storytelling across the broadcast industry.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</CaseStudyLayout>
